@startuml
actor Developer
participant "VS Code" as VSCode
participant "Black Formatter" as Black
participant "Integrated Terminal" as Terminal
participant "Python Interpreter" as Python

Developer -> VSCode: Write or edit Python code
Developer -> VSCode: Save file
VSCode -> Black: Run formatter on save
Black --> VSCode: Return formatted code
Developer -> Terminal: Run python script.py
Terminal -> Python: Execute script
Python --> Developer: Display output
@enduml